{"tid":109109,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十大巴基斯坦人 民族性特徵  學者遂一點評","createTime":"2017-02-05T17:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T11:15:24.000Z","uid":82646,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"568a4c805daf72d02173b88b6da2dcfc4317a129","tid":109109,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>學者S. Anwer: 十大巴基斯坦裔民族性特徵  (已翻譯為中文)</strong><br />\n<br />\n10 troublesome traits of the average Pakistani  By Sohail Anwer<br />\n<br />\n1.  巴基斯坦人不喜歡用腦去想該做什麼, 多盲從體制. 但對於自己財產包括妻兒擁有絕   對話事權<br />\n<br />\n2.  巴基斯坦人從不認錯， 因為他們認錯等於對自己家族的一種詛咒<br />\n<br />\n3. 巴基斯坦人幾乎可以以伊斯蘭教的名義做任何事情，例如殺害某人，但永遠不會為了社會的共同利益或婦女的權利而行使正義<br />\n<br />\n4.  大多巴基斯坦人認為所有事應為他們而來，而非相反去主動爭取<br />\n<br />\n5.  普遍巴基斯坦人清楚知道民事和刑事事項上的憲法和法律權利，但逃避義務，以及如何以負責任的方式行使這些權利。<br />\n<br />\n6.  一般巴基斯坦人知道問題原因及補救辦法，但除非他相信他也將在解決過程中得到利益，否則永遠不會前行半寸去解決它。 此外，他永遠不會試圖阻止一宗可惡的罪行，除非受害者是他的兄弟姐妹，父母或任何密切的關係。<br />\n<br />\n7.   一般巴基斯坦人認為貪腐是他的權利，以追求幸福。 巴基斯坦的毒販和大多數公務員是這方面的一個實際例子。<br />\n<br />\n8.   巴基斯坦人的愛國的想法爛透了。 愛國只局限於祖家領地。 如果旁遮普人的本土人相信， 設塞拉基省是為對抗旁遮普邦的陰謀論，他會堅持，即使它會傷害巴基斯坦長期。<br />\n<br />\n9.   上左位的幸運巴基斯坦人傾向於裙帶主義，取而代之的是用裙帶主義取代競爭主義已經成為巴基斯坦文化的一個組成部分。<br />\n<br />\n10.  巴基斯坦人對司法的概念是令人討厭的。 我們賄賂辦事員和法院官員拖了六個月的案件100年。 如果罪犯名聲勢力大，受害者比罪犯無助和弱勢，社會更傾向贊同施暴者而不是弱方受害者。 在村莊里，婦女是財產，只能因為一個部落的男性成員做錯了而可以交換或侵犯。<br />\n<br />\nThere are many other problems facing Pakistan, but in my view, these are the 10 main problems we face as a nation. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://blogs.tribune.com.pk/story/6109/10-troublesome-traits-of-the-average-pakistani/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblogs.tribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F6109%2F10-troublesome-traits-of-the-average-pakistani%2F&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=960981e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://blogs.tribune.com.pk/story/6109/10-troublesome-traits-of-the-average-pakistani/</a>"},{"pid":"bad7b57c84583649674754c56b18295fff14a17b","tid":109109,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T23:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cc8822d65747dea5e1081202e37f5a00f51c8f","tid":109109,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T23:38:05.000Z","msg":"咁似支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1d0932426a6d83179a1eca15887e91dacd4dc7","tid":109109,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T23:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁似支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比支那更貪 佢地以為地球為佢轉呢d on9諗法"},{"pid":"1895f9bf65578546486e91dd7b0d13d1513a6ef5","tid":109109,"uid":21744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T23:44:23.000Z","msg":"四個字低等人種"},{"pid":"6f0dccd3c392e189f46792fa47d94a2ffcc01c15","tid":109109,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T23:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁似支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又懶又貪又野蠻<br />\n仲衰過支那人"},{"pid":"5cea5929916cc33ef5c38e8f9187d73f43f7c13f","tid":109109,"uid":12232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T00:15:00.000Z","msg":"仲等我入黎睇性特徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b595e536d530c95953563b6abecab77956b624","tid":109109,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T00:27:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d60c7b29ce4d34a5502d9a9a589eadeb73a46ebd","tid":109109,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T00:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲等我入黎睇性特徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa